items.title: CoStar Group adds millions to network by acquiring ForRent
items.summary:
CoStar Group, Inc. the leading provider of commercial real estate information, analytics and online marketplaces, announced today that it plans to acquire ForRent, a division of Dominion Enterprises, pursuant to a definitive agreement for $350 million in cash and $35 million in CoStar Group stock.
